message.body: Oh boy. I hope my stupidity is cute to you. Jason liked that I couldn't remember all the baseball terminology. I was trying to stay a little dumb for him but I'm actually trying to understand at least a little for you.
I love you Keith. Thanks for being in my life.
Got a signal for a second and just got three of your texts...I love you too and im really glad you're in my life :-) XOXOXO!
